  "lyrics": "I feel the fire from the nights we knew Every color's gonna paint me new I feel the fire from the nights we knew Every color's gonna paint me new I got that 80's in my soul Life from yesterday makes me whole We all in love anyway I shout tomorrow's mine Tomorrow is all we got from the divine Arcade hills morning heat Silver spots on the concrete streets Everywhere's a shaded shoot Sweaty pea-sky and an electric blues I feel the fire from the nights we knew Every color's gonna paint me new I feel all the desire from the fire Every color's a new shade No reason to know that I got that 80's in my soul Life from yesterday makes me whole We all in love anyway I shout tomorrow's mine Tomorrow's mine You're in love and away we shine Yeah, grow, grow, never let it go The cold light guide me home Glow, baby, glow Watch the future grow From the colors that I've always known The one that keeps me in your zone Let it show, yeah I got that 80's in my soul Life from yesterday makes me whole We all in love anyway I shout tomorrow's mine Tomorrow's all mine Won't let anybody take that now Thanks for watching!",
