    },
    {
      "end": 90.9800033569336,
      "text": "Tomorrow's mine You're in love and away we shine",
      "start": 85.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 98.9800033569336,
      "text": "Yeah, grow, grow, never let it go The cold light guide me home",
